        <item>
            <title>【评测】M4 MacBook Air 天蓝色新款，实机相片多角度观赏 + Apple 卖大包效能大提升</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/11/m4-macbook-air-2/notebook/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=m4-macbook-air-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/11/m4-macbook-air-2/notebook/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 11 Mar 2025 13:00:09 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动电脑]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[MacBook Air]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1296963</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 正式推出 M4 MacBook Air，在同一个机壳之下，继 Apple M2、M3 处理器之后推出到第 3 个升级－－全新 MacBook Air 搭载 M4 处理器。相信好多朋友都喜欢当年 M2 MacBook Air 新机壳四四方方，诚实厚重设计，而且所有配色都比较浅色，清淡但够高贵显雅。今年 Apple 更加推出新色「天蓝色」，我们以下会给大家多看新机的相片，当然也会详细介绍与评测。</p><p><span class="Apple-converted-space"></span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296966" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00728-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00728-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00728.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296967" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00708-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00708-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00708.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>天蓝色新色真机图片共赏<span class="Apple-converted-space"></span>手指纹黏附情况已有改善</h2><p>今次得到 Apple 协助我们借来了最新「天蓝色」M4 MacBook Air 新机。同大家在 Apple 官网看到的图片相比，我们看到实物更加高贵大方，最主要是它的颜色并不「过于抢眼」，在充足的光线下更似有点染蓝的银色。而在室内灯光下，你会看到银色底上面渗出粉蓝色。同之前的星光色一样，蓝色色调不会过于抢眼。</p><p>M4 MacBook Air 同样使用抗指纹表面涂层。过去 M2 MacBook Air 时其午夜暗色被用家指容易吸手指纹，即使在天气干燥的环境之下，都是好易吸手指模。而在今次浅色机身上，不容易黏上手手指纹，即使黏上也较容易使用布质材料抹去。但当然它并非完全抗指纹，如果你的手指充满油脂的话，还是先抹干手。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296968" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00706-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00706-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00706.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296969" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00712-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00712-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00712.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296970" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00716-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00716-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00716.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296971" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00722-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00722-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00722.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>大家看到现时 Apple 只提供 M4 版 MacBook Air，去除了过往保留旧版的选项。而升级 M4 处理器后售价依然维持 HK$7,999 起。新机最大特点是 CPU 处理器由 8 核心升到 10 核心，在基本配置下统一记忆体有 16GB、记忆体频宽由上代 100GB/s 增至 120GB/s。用家可付费添置多至 32GB 记忆体，比上代多了 8GB。对于需要进行影片剪辑，但又不至于买 MacBook Pro 的朋友，便有更弹性的选择。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296972" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00728-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00728-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00728-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296973" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00734-694x414.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="414" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00734-694x414.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00734-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296975" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05214-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05214-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc05214-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲我们发现在不同灯光环境之下，天蓝色 MacBook Air 又会变成较偏向银的色调</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296965" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00739-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00739-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00739.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲在太阳光底下，又有另一个独特样貌</p><p>Apple 并未有将最先进 Thunderbolt 5 下放到 Air 系列，但对绝大部份 Air 用户来说，两个 Thunderbolt 4 的 USB-C 插头已经十分够用，因为它已经兼容 USB4 标准。而香港一般电脑用家，在市面买到的硬碟、SSD、快闪手指其实大多数都是 Thunderbolt 3/USB4/USB 3.2 Gen 2，基本上不是问题。</p><p><span class="Apple-converted-space"></span></p><p><span class="Apple-converted-space"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296976" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00734-1-694x414.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="414" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00734-1-694x414.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00734-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></span></p><p><span class="Apple-converted-space"></span></p><h2>效能提升 25.6% 非常显著</h2><p>今代 M4 处理器最大特色是增加了 2 个 CPU 核心，处理器搭配 10 核心 CPU、10 核心 GPU，用电增强但 Apple 也在电池上面轻轻加大了容量，由 52.6 瓦时加大到 53.8 瓦时。应用上我们不觉它比 M3 版的 MacBook Air 更耗电，新旧型号电池耗用基本上持平。</p><p>实际在跑分方面，今代 M4 处理器在 Geekbench 6 的基本单核分数为 3719 分，比对上代提升达 23.6%，可说是一个非常大的升幅；多核分数更加有 14846 分，比对上代提升 25.6％。今代 M4 MacBook Air 可说是非常有诚意。</p><table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tbody><tr><td valign="top"></td><td valign="top">M4 MacBook Air</td><td valign="top">M3 MacBook Air</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">单核心测试</td><td valign="top">3719 (+23.6%)</td><td valign="top">3009</td></tr><tr><td valign="top">多核心测试</td><td valign="top">14846 (+25.6%)</td><td valign="top">11817</td></tr></tbody></table><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/11/m4-macbook-air-2/notebook/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Sony 测试 AI 驱动游戏角色，已将《Horizon》 Aloy AI 化</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/11/sony-playstation-ai-characters-aloy-horizon-forbidden-west-prototype/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sony-playstation-ai-characters-aloy-horizon-forbidden-west-prototype</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/11/sony-playstation-ai-characters-aloy-horizon-forbidden-west-prototype/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 11 Mar 2025 12:55:13 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1296815</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>SONY 正研发人工智能驱动的 PlayStation 游戏角色，先导项目以《Horizon Forbidden West》的主角 Aloy 为原型。该技术由 SONY 先进技术小组与 Guerrilla Games 合作开发，已于内部展示。首个演示于 2024 年前完成，并于 11 月东京技术交流展览展出进阶版本。</p><p>SONY 先进技术小组开发的 AI 版 Aloy 可透过语音指令与玩家对话，采用 OpenAI 的 Whisper 进行语音转文字，结合 GPT-4 及 Llama 3 处理对话与决策。语音生成则用上 SONY 自家的 Emotional Voice Synthesis（EVS），面部动画由内部 Mockingbird 技术支援。虽然演示在 PC 上运行，但 SONY 已测试于 PS5 上执行部分功能。</p><p>网上资料显示，SONY 早在 2025 年 2 月提交专利，探索 AI 助手为玩家提供游戏指引，显示其对 AI 技术的长期投入。此此 AI 原型展示 SONY 在游戏互动技术上的突破。若成功整合至 PS5 或未来平台，可提升玩家体验。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/news/626695/sony-playstation-ai-characters-aloy-horizon-forbidden-west-prototype">The Verge</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/11/sony-playstation-ai-characters-aloy-horizon-forbidden-west-prototype/ai/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>HTC Wildfire E5 Plus 750 元有找进军平价市场，沈寂多时终于有新机</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/11/htc-wild-fire-e5-plus/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=htc-wild-fire-e5-plus</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/11/htc-wild-fire-e5-plus/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 11 Mar 2025 12:25:38 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[htc]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1296844</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>台湾知名手机品牌 HTC 在沉寂多时后，近日于海外市场推出新机 HTC Wildfire E5 Plus。这款入门级智能手机于 2025 年 3 月在越南及泰国等东南亚地区上市，主打大萤幕、长续航及高像素相机，价格亲民，在越南售价仅 2,379,000 VND（约港币 735 元），锁定基础使用需求的消费者。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296887" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus6-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus6-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus6-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus6.jpg 800w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>HTC Wildfire E5 Plus 配备 6.745 吋 HD+ 萤幕，支援 90Hz 更新率，提供流畅的视觉体验，适合日常浏览社交媒体或观看影片。电池容量达 5000mAh，能满足一天甚至两天的使用需求，对于不常充电的用家而言颇具吸引力。据《Gizmo China》报道，该机在越南售价仅 2,379,000 VND（约港币 735 元），性价比突出，定位清晰。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296885" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus4-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus4-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus4-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus4.jpg 800w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296886" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus9-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus9-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus9-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus9.jpg 800w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>相机方面，HTC Wildfire E5 Plus 搭载 50MP 主镜头及 2MP 景深镜头，足以应付日常拍摄，前置则为 16MP 镜头，满足自拍及视像通话需要。处理器采用 Unisoc T606，搭配 6GB RAM 及 128GB ROM，支援 microSD 卡扩充，基本运行流畅，但不适合大型游戏。系统预载 Android 14，并保留 3.5mm 耳机孔及 USB Type-C 接口，功能实用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296888" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus2-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus2-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus2-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/htcwildfiree5plus2.jpg 800w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p>HTC Wildfire E5 Plus 的推出显示品牌有意在东南亚市场寻求突破，凭借低价策略或能吸引新兴市场消费者，未来能否扩展至其他地区仍视乎市场反馈及品牌策略调整。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1296883" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481456790_1090648873-694x273.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="273" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481456790_1090648873-694x273.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/481456790_1090648873-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.gizmochina.com/2025/03/09/htc-wildfire-e5-plus-launched-with-6-74-inch-display-50mp-main-camera/">Gizmo China</a>、<a href="https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61573908089181">HTC Thailand</a>、<a href="https://www.gsmarena.com/htc_wildfire_e_plus-11948.php">gsmarena</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
