            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1293255</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>香港人热爱行山，但山区信号覆盖有限，通讯中断的情况时有发生。中国移动香港在 2025 年行山节上推出的「北斗短信」服务，为行山者提供在无地面网络覆盖环境下的通讯保障，确保行山人士无论身处何处，都可与外界保持联系。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/hkt.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294390" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/hkt-694x391.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/hkt-694x391.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/hkt.jpeg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/unwire-1740640335-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294407" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/unwire-1740640335-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/unwire-1740640335-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/unwire-1740640335-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲中移动香港行山节之中，亦有应用「北斗短信」技术</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/unwire-1740640340-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294408" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/unwire-1740640340-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/unwire-1740640340-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/unwire-1740640340-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲北斗体验台让公众亲身测试发送短信</p><h2 class="p3">无信号环境下求助与报平安</h2><p class="p3">「北斗短信」依托中国自主研发的北斗衞星系统，即使在手机无信号的情况下，满足紧急通讯要求，透过特定终端发送带有定位资讯的文字短信。北斗短信允许用户最多发送 20 个汉字（可发送位置，占用 2 个汉字）、最多接收 6 个汉字。行山者在迷路、受伤或遇上突发情况时，能迅速发出求救信息，并提供确切位置，协助救援单位及时应对。行山者亦可利用此服务向家人报平安，减少亲友担忧。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/1062609286121390171-scaled.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1294399 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/1062609286121390171-694x463.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/1062609286121390171-694x463.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/1062609286121390171-scaled.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/c8e9713c75ba411bad2d-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293431" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/c8e9713c75ba411bad2d-1-694x357.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="357" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/c8e9713c75ba411bad2d-1-694x357.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/c8e9713c75ba411bad2d-1.jpg 1080w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲「北斗短信」运作示意图</p><div>如何发送北斗短信：用户进入北斗衞星短信界面，编辑内容后根据提示进行搜星发送，至多可发送 20 个汉字（可发送位置，占用 2 个汉字），最多同时向 4 个用户发送。接收北斗短信的用户将收到短信内容。</div><div></div><div></div><div>如何回复北斗短信：客户在接收到北斗短信后可在 3 天内编辑短信进行回复，最长 6 个汉字。北斗短信用户进入北斗衞星短信界面，点击接收按钮，根据寻星界面指引接收回复短信。</div><div></div><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/q12-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1293437" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/q12-1-694x370.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="370" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/q12-1-694x370.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/q12-1.jpg 983w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2 class="p3">简单易用<b></b>无需更换手机号码</h2><p class="p3">与传统衞星通讯设备不同，「北斗短信」的使用方式更为简便。行山者无需额外购买昂贵的专业设备，只需透过普通手机，启用北斗短信服务，即可在无信号时发送文字及位置资讯。这种「不换卡、不换号」的设计，大大降低了使用门槛，适合所有行山爱好者。</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
